   composition of fungi, the following isotope-enrichment factors (epsilon,
   mean +/- SD) of the fungi relative to substrates were observed:
   epsilon(ectomycorrhizal fungi/litter) = 6.1 +/- 0.4 parts per thousand
   N-15
