   C-13
   epsilon(wood decomposing fung/wood) = -0.6 +/- 0.7 parts per thousand
   N-15
   epsilon(wood decomposing fungi/wood) = 3.5 +/- 0.9 parts per thousand,
   C-13
   The basis of isotope fractionation in C metabolism from mood to
   wood-decomposing fungus is discussed.}},
